{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775849561771,"sessionID":"ses_2871fef59ffeLKcpssOo7g7lYG","part":{"id":"prt_d78e0ab16001v0aJpnNip0Zr5v","messageID":"msg_d78e08e1b001Ivdg1MT1E6kn2C","sessionID":"ses_2871fef59ffeLKcpssOo7g7lYG","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_3f53e63c2d9244dda1bc5f6d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-011\n- **Module**: `pkg/router`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Draft\n- **Base**: AR-010 (Session Management)\n\n## 1. 概述\n\n本设计文档聚焦于 **JWT 认证与签发** 功能，为 `pkg/router` 模块增加基于 JWT 的身份验证和令牌管理能力。该功能是 AR-010 会话管理的扩展，提供安全的 API 访问控制。\n\n### 1.1 目标\n\n- 实现 JWT Token 验证（支持 HS256、RS256 算法）\n- 实现 JWT Token 签发（登录接口）\n- 实现 Token 刷新接口\n- 支持可配置的 JWT 参数（Issuer、Audience、Expiry）\n- 提供 JWT 指标监控\n\n### 1.2 依赖\n\n- `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` — JWT 令牌处理\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router` — 现有路由模块\n\n---\n\n## 2. 架构设计\n\n### 2.1 整体架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         Router Server (pkg/router)                       │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐    │\n│  │   JWT       │→ │  Auth       │→ │  Rate Limit │→ │   Proxy     │    │\n│  │ Middleware  │  │ Middleware  │  │  Middleware  │  │   Handler   │    │\n│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘    │\n│         │                                                                    │\n│  ┌──────▼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐         │\n│  │                    JWT Manager                               │         │\n│  │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐         │         │\n│  │  │   Token     │  │   Token     │  │   Key       │         │         │\n│  │  │  Validation│  │  Issuance   │  │  Management │         │         │\n│  │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘         │         │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘         │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 2.2 组件职责\n\n| 组件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|\n| `JWTMiddleware` | 拦截请求，提取并验证 JWT Token |\n| `JWTManager` | 核心 JWT 操作：签发、验证、刷新 |\n| `KeyManager` | 密钥管理（HS256 对称密钥、RS256 非对称密钥） |\n| `LoginHandler` | 处理用户登录，签发 Token |\n| `RefreshHandler` | 处理 Token 刷新 |\n\n### 2.3 数据流\n\n```\n1. 客户端请求进入 Router\n   │\n2. JWTMiddleware 检查公开端点\n   ├── 公开端点 → 跳过验证，继续处理\n   │\n3. JWTMiddleware 提取 Token\n   ├── 从 Header: Authorization: Bearer <token>\n   ├── 或从 Query: ?token=<token>\n   │\n4. JWTManager 验证 Token\n   ├── 检查签名\n   ├── 检查过期时间\n   ├── 检查 Issuer\n   ├── 检查 Audience\n   │\n5. 验证通过 → 将 Claims 写入 Context → 传递给下游 Handler\n   │\n6. 验证失败 → 返回 401 Unauthorized\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. 数据结构\n\n### 3.1 JWT 配置\n\n```go\n// JWTConfig holds JWT-specific configuration\ntype JWTConfig struct {\n    Enabled         bool          // Enable JWT authentication (default: false)\n    Algorithm       string        // Algorithm: \"HS256\" or \"RS256\" (default: \"HS256\")\n    Secret          string        // Secret key for HS256\n    PrivateKeyPath  string        // Path to RSA private key for RS256\n    PublicKeyPath   string        // Path to RSA public key for RS256\n    Issuer          string        // Token issuer (default: \"agentcube\")\n    Audience        []string      // Expected audience claims\n    Expiration      time.Duration // Token expiration (default: 1h)\n    RefreshExpiration time.Duration // Refresh token expiration (default: 24h)\n    ClockSkew       time.Duration // Clock skew tolerance (default: 30s)\n    AllowQueryParam bool          // Allow token in query parameter (default: false)\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 JWT 声明\n\n```go\n// Claims represents standard JWT claims\ntype Claims struct {\n    jwt.RegisteredClaims\n    // Custom claims\n    Roles     []string          `json:\"roles,omitempty\"`\n    TenantID  string            `json:\"tenant_id,omitempty\"`\n    Namespace string            `json:\"namespace,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// UserCredentials represents login request\ntype UserCredentials struct {\n    Username string `json:\"username\" binding:\"required\"`\n    Password string `json:\"password\" binding:\"required\"`\n}\n\n// LoginResponse represents login response\ntype LoginResponse struct {\n    AccessToken  string `json:\"access_token\"`\n    RefreshToken string `json:\"refresh_token\"`\n    TokenType    string `json:\"token_type\"`\n    ExpiresIn    int64  `json:\"expires_in\"`\n}\n\n// TokenRefreshRequest represents refresh token request\ntype TokenRefreshRequest struct {\n    RefreshToken string `json:\"refresh_token\" binding:\"required\"`\n}\n```\n\n### 3.3 JWT 管理器\n\n```go\n// JWTManager handles JWT token operations\ntype JWTManager struct {\n    config          *JWTConfig\n    secretKey       []byte\n    privateKey      *rsa.PrivateKey\n    publicKey       *rsa.PublicKey\n    metrics         *JWTMetrics\n    userValidator   UserValidator\n    mu              sync.RWMutex\n}\n\n// UserValidator validates user credentials\ntype UserValidator interface {\n    Validate(username, password string) (*UserClaims, error)\n}\n\n// UserClaims represents authenticated user info\ntype UserClaims struct {\n    Username  string\n    Roles     []string\n    TenantID  string\n    Namespace string\n}\n```\n\n### 3.4 更新配置结构\n\n```go\n// Config (extended from AR-010)\ntype Config struct {\n    // ... existing fields ...\n    \n    // JWT settings\n    JWT JWTConfig // JWT configuration\n}\n\n// DefaultConfig returns config with JWT defaults\nfunc DefaultConfig() *Config {\n    return &Config{\n        // ... existing defaults ...\n        JWT: JWTConfig{\n            Enabled:         false,\n            Algorithm:       \"HS256\",\n            Secret:          \"\",\n            Issuer:          \"agentcube\",\n            Audience:        nil,\n            Expiration:      1 * time.Hour,\n            RefreshExpiration: 24 * time.Hour,\n            ClockSkew:       30 * time.Second,\n            AllowQueryParam: false,\n        },\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. API 合约\n\n### 4.1 新增端点\n\n| Method | Path | Middleware | Handler | Description |\n|--------|------|------------|---------|-------------|\n| POST | `/login` | none | `handleLogin` | 用户登录，签发 Token |\n| POST | `/refresh` | none | `handleRefresh` | 刷新 Token |\n| GET | `/validate` | JWT | `handleValidate` | 验证当前 Token |\n\n### 4.2 受保护端点（需 JWT）\n\n| Method | Path | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/*path` | AgentRuntime 代理 |\n| POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/*path` | AgentRuntime 代理 |\n| GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/*path` | CodeInterpreter 代理 |\n| POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/*path` | CodeInterpreter 代理 |\n\n### 4.3 公开端点（跳过 JWT）\n\n- `/health/live`\n- `/health/ready`\n- `/metrics`\n- `/login`\n- `/refresh`\n\n### 4.4 登录请求/响应\n\n```json\n// POST /login - Request\n{\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"secret\"\n}\n\n// Response - Success\n{\n    \"access_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n    \"refresh_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n    \"token_type\": \"Bearer\",\n    \"expires_in\": 3600\n}\n\n// Response - Error\n{\n    \"error\": \"invalid credentials\",\n    \"code\": \"ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIALS\",\n    \"requestId\": \"req-xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4.5 Token 刷新请求/响应\n\n```json\n// POST /refresh - Request\n{\n    \"refresh_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\"\n}\n\n// Response - Success\n{\n    \"access_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n    \"token_type\": \"Bearer\",\n    \"expires_in\": 3600\n}\n```\n\n### 4.6 错误响应\n\n| Status Code | Description | Error Code |\n|-------------|-------------|------------|\n| 200 | Success | - |\n| 400 | Bad Request (malformed token) | `ERR_MALFORMED_TOKEN` |\n| 401 | Unauthorized (invalid/expired token) | `ERR_UNAUTHORIZED` |\n| 401 | Invalid credentials | `ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIALS` |\n| 401 | Invalid audience | `ERR_INVALID_AUDIENCE` |\n| 401 | Invalid issuer | `ERR_INVALID_ISSUER` |\n| 401 | Invalid signature | `ERR_INVALID_SIGNATURE` |\n| 401 | Token expired | `ERR_TOKEN_EXPIRED` |\n| 401 | Invalid refresh token | `ERR_INVALID_REFRESH_TOKEN` |\n\n---\n\n## 5. 实现细节\n\n### 5.1 JWT 验证流程\n\n```go\nfunc (m *JWTManager) ValidateToken(tokenString string) (*Claims, error) {\n    // Parse token without validation first\n    token, _, err := jwt.NewParser().ParseUnverified(tokenString, &Claims{})\n    if err != nil {\n        return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"%w: %v\", ErrMalformedToken, err)\n    }\n    \n    // Select validation key based on algorithm\n    var validationKey interface{}\n    switch m.config.Algorithm {\n    case \"HS256\":\n        validationKey = m.secretKey\n    case \"RS256\":\n        validationKey = m.publicKey\n    }\n    \n    // Validate token\n    claims := &Claims{}\n    token, err = jwt.ParseWithClaims(tokenString, claims, func(token *jwt.Token) (interface{}, error) {\n        // Verify signing method\n        switch m.config.Algorithm {\n        case \"HS256\":\n            _, ok := token.Method.(*jwt.SigningMethodHMAC)\n            if !ok {\n                return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"%w: unexpected signing method: %v\", ErrInvalidSignature, token.Header[\"alg\"])\n            }\n        case \"RS256\":\n            _, ok := token.Method.(*jwt.SigningMethodRSA)\n            if !ok {\n                return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"%w: unexpected signing method: %v\", ErrInvalidSignature, token.Header[\"alg\"])\n            }\n        }\n        return validationKey, nil\n    }, jwt.WithIssuer(m.config.Issuer),\n       jwt.WithAudience(m.config.Audience...),\n       jwt.WithClockSkew(m.config.ClockSkew))\n    \n    if err != nil {\n        if errors.Is(err, jwt.ErrTokenExpired) {\n            return nil, ErrTokenExpired\n        }\n        if errors.Is(err, jwt.ErrTokenSignatureInvalid) {\n            return nil, ErrInvalidSignature\n        }\n        return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"%w: %v\", ErrUnauthorized, err)\n    }\n    \n    return claims, nil\n}\n```\n\n### 5.2 JWT 签发流程\n\n```go\nfunc (m *JWTManager) IssueToken(user *UserClaims) (string, error) {\n    now := time.Now()\n    \n    claims := Claims{\n        RegisteredClaims: jwt.RegisteredClaims{\n            ExpiresAt: jwt.NewNumericDate(now.Add(m.config.Expiration)),\n            IssuedAt:  jwt.NewNumericDate(now),\n            NotBefore: jwt.NewNumericDate(now),\n            Issuer:    m.config.Issuer,\n            ID:        uuid.New().String(),\n        },\n        Roles:     user.Roles,\n        TenantID:  user.TenantID,\n        Namespace: user.Namespace,\n    }\n    \n    // Add audience if configured\n    if len(m.config.Audience) > 0 {\n        claims.Audience = m.config.Audience\n    }\n    \n    // Sign token based on algorithm\n    var tokenString string\n    var err error\n    \n    switch m.config.Algorithm {\n    case \"HS256\":\n        tokenString, err = jwt.NewWithClaims(jwt.SigningMethodHS256, claims).SignedString(m.secretKey)\n    case \"RS256\":\n        tokenString, err = jwt.NewWithClaims(jwt.SigningMethodRS256, claims).SignedString(m.privateKey)\n    default:\n        return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"unsupported algorithm: %s\", m.config.Algorithm)\n    }\n    \n    if err != nil {\n        return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"failed to sign token: %w\", err)\n    }\n    \n    m.metrics.IssuedTotal.Inc()\n    return tokenString, nil\n}\n```\n\n### 5.3 中间件实现\n\n```go\n// JWTMiddleware creates JWT authentication middleware\nfunc JWTMiddleware(manager *JWTManager, publicPaths []string) Middleware {\n    publicPathSet := make(map[string]bool)\n    for _, path := range publicPaths {\n        publicPathSet[path] = true\n    }\n    \n    return func(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n        return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n            // Check if public path\n            if publicPathSet[r.URL.Path] {\n                next.ServeHTTP(w, r)\n                return\n            }\n            \n            // Extract token\n            tokenString, err := extractToken(r, manager.config.AllowQueryParam)\n            if err != nil {\n                http.Error(w, err.Error(), http.StatusBadRequest)\n                return\n            }\n            \n            // Validate token\n            claims, err := manager.ValidateToken(tokenString)\n            if err != nil {\n                manager.metrics.ValidationErrorsTotal.WithLabelValues(getErrorType(err)).Inc()\n                http.Error(w, \"Unauthorized\", http.StatusUnauthorized)\n                return\n            }\n            \n            // Add claims to context\n            ctx := context.WithValue(r.Context(), ContextKeyClaims, claims)\n            ctx = context.WithValue(ctx, ContextKeyUsername, claims.Subject)\n            \n            manager.metrics.ValidatedTotal.WithLabelValues(\"success\").Inc()\n            next.ServeHTTP(w, r.WithContext(ctx))\n        })\n    }\n}\n\nfunc extractToken(r *http.Request, allowQueryParam bool) (string, error) {\n    // Try Authorization header first\n    authHeader := r.Header.Get(\"Authorization\")\n    if authHeader != \"\" {\n        parts := strings.SplitN(authHeader, \" \", 2)\n        if len(parts) == 2 && strings.ToLower(parts[0]) == \"bearer\" {\n            return parts[1], nil\n        }\n    }\n    \n    // Try query parameter if allowed\n    if allowQueryParam {\n        if token := r.URL.Query().Get(\"token\"); token != \"\" {\n            return token, nil\n        }\n    }\n    \n    return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"%w: no token found\", ErrMalformedToken)\n}\n```\n\n### 5.4 登录处理器\n\n```go\nfunc (m *JWTManager) HandleLogin(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    var creds UserCredentials\n    if err := json.NewDecoder(r.Body).Decode(&creds); err != nil {\n        writeError(w, \"bad request\", \"ERR_BAD_REQUEST\", http.StatusBadRequest)\n        return\n    }\n    \n    // Validate credentials\n    user, err := m.userValidator.Validate(creds.Username, creds.Password)\n    if err != nil {\n        writeError(w, \"invalid credentials\", \"ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIALS\", http.StatusUnauthorized)\n        return\n    }\n    \n    // Issue tokens\n    accessToken, err := m.IssueToken(user)\n    if err != nil {\n        writeError(w, \"failed to issue token\", \"ERR_TOKEN_ISSUANCE_FAILED\", http.StatusInternalServerError)\n        return\n    }\n    \n    refreshToken, err := m.IssueRefreshToken(user)\n    if err != nil {\n        writeError(w, \"failed to issue refresh token\", \"ERR_TOKEN_ISSUANCE_FAILED\", http.StatusInternalServerError)\n        return\n    }\n    \n    response := LoginResponse{\n        AccessToken:  accessToken,\n        RefreshToken: refreshToken,\n        TokenType:    \"Bearer\",\n        ExpiresIn:    int64(m.config.Expiration.Seconds()),\n    }\n    \n    w.Header().Set(\"Content-Type\", \"application/json\")\n    json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(response)\n}\n```\n\n### 5.5 密钥管理\n\n```go\n// KeyManager handles JWT key loading and management\ntype KeyManager struct {\n    config *JWTConfig\n}\n\nfunc (km *KeyManager) LoadKeys() error {\n    switch km.config.Algorithm {\n    case \"HS256\":\n        if km.config.Secret == \"\" {\n            return fmt.Errorf(\"JWT secret is required for HS256\")\n        }\n        km.config.Secret = os.Getenv(\"JWT_SECRET\") // Override from env if set\n    case \"RS256\":\n        if km.config.PrivateKeyPath == \"\" || km.config.PublicKeyPath == \"\" {\n            return fmt.Errorf(\"JWT key paths are required for RS256\")\n        }\n        \n        privateKeyData, err := os.ReadFile(km.config.PrivateKeyPath)\n        if err != nil {\n            return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to read private key: %w\", err)\n        }\n        \n        privateKey, err := jwt.ParseRSAPrivateKeyFromPEM(privateKeyData)\n        if err != nil {\n            return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse private key: %w\", err)\n        }\n        \n        publicKeyData, err := os.ReadFile(km.config.PublicKeyPath)\n        if err != nil {\n            return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to read public key: %w\", err)\n        }\n        \n        publicKey, err := jwt.ParseRSAPublicKeyFromPEM(publicKeyData)\n        if err != nil {\n            return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse public key: %w\", err)\n        }\n    }\n    \n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. 错误处理\n\n### 6.1 错误类型\n\n```go\n// JWT Errors\nvar (\n    ErrMalformedToken     = errors.New(\"malformed token\")\n    ErrInvalidSignature   = errors.New(\"invalid signature\")\n    ErrTokenExpired       = errors.New(\"token expired\")\n    ErrInvalidAudience    = errors.New(\"invalid audience\")\n    ErrInvalidIssuer      = errors.New(\"invalid issuer\")\n    ErrUnauthorized       = errors.New(\"unauthorized\")\n    ErrInvalidCredentials = errors.New(\"invalid credentials\")\n    ErrInvalidRefreshToken = errors.New(\"invalid refresh token\")\n)\n\n// Error codes\nconst (\n    ErrCodeMalformedToken      = \"ERR_MALFORMED_TOKEN\"\n    ErrCodeInvalidSignature   = \"ERR_INVALID_SIGNATURE\"\n    ErrCodeTokenExpired        = \"ERR_TOKEN_EXPIRED\"\n    ErrCodeInvalidAudience    = \"ERR_INVALID_AUDIENCE\"\n    ErrCodeInvalidIssuer       = \"ERR_INVALID_ISSUER\"\n    ErrCodeUnauthorized       = \"ERR_UNAUTHORIZED\"\n    ErrCodeInvalidCredentials  = \"ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIALS\"\n    ErrCodeInvalidRefreshToken = \"ERR_INVALID_REFRESH_TOKEN\"\n)\n```\n\n### 6.2 错误处理策略\n\n| 错误场景 | HTTP 状态码 | 处理策略 |\n|----------|-------------|----------|\n| Token 格式错误 | 400 | 记录错误，返回 \"malformed token\" |\n| Token 签名无效 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid signature\" |\n| Token 已过期 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"token expired\" |\n| Audience 不匹配 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid audience\" |\n| Issuer 不匹配 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid issuer\" |\n| 无效凭证 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid credentials\" |\n| 无效刷新 Token | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid refresh token\" |\n\n---\n\n## 7. 监控指标\n\n### 7.1 Prometheus 指标\n\n| Metric | Type | Labels | Description |\n|--------|------|--------|-------------|\n| `jwt_validated_total` | Counter | result (success/error) | JWT validation count |\n| `jwt_issued_total` | Counter | - | JWT token issuance count |\n| `jwt_refreshed_total` | Counter | result | JWT token refresh count |\n| `jwt_validation_errors_total` | Counter | error_type | JWT validation errors |\n\n### 7.2 指标实现\n\n```go\ntype JWTMetrics struct {\n    ValidatedTotal        *prometheus.CounterVec\n    IssuedTotal          prometheus.Counter\n    RefreshedTotal       *prometheus.CounterVec\n    ValidationErrorsTotal *prometheus.CounterVec\n}\n\nfunc NewJWTMetrics() *JWTMetrics {\n    return &JWTMetrics{\n        ValidatedTotal: prometheus.NewCounterVec(\n            prometheus.CounterOpts{\n                Name: \"jwt_validated_total\",\n                Help: \"Total number of JWT validations\",\n            },\n            []string{\"result\"},\n        ),\n        IssuedTotal: prometheus.NewCounter(\n            prometheus.CounterOpts{\n                Name: \"jwt_issued_total\",\n                Help: \"Total number of JWT tokens issued\",\n            },\n        ),\n        RefreshedTotal: prometheus.NewCounterVec(\n            prometheus.CounterOpts{\n                Name: \"jwt_refreshed_total\",\n                Help: \"Total number of JWT token refreshes\",\n            },\n            []string{\"result\"},\n        ),\n        ValidationErrorsTotal: prometheus.NewCounterVec(\n            prometheus.CounterOpts{\n                Name: \"jwt_validation_errors_total\",\n                Help: \"Total number of JWT validation errors\",\n            },\n            []string{\"error_type\"},\n        ),\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 8. 测试策略\n\n### 8.1 单元测试\n\n| 模块 | 测试重点 |\n|------|----------|\n| `JWTManager` | Token 签发、验证、刷新、算法切换 |\n| `KeyManager` | 密钥加载、HS256/RS256 切换 |\n| `JWTMiddleware` | Token 提取、公开端点跳过、Context 传递 |\n| `LoginHandler` | 登录成功、失败、错误处理 |\n| `RefreshHandler` | 刷新成功、过期 Token 拒绝 |\n\n### 8.2 测试场景\n\n| 场景 | 预期结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| 有效 JWT Token 验证 | 验证成功，Claims 正确解析 |\n| 过期 JWT Token 验证 | 返回 ErrTokenExpired |\n| 无效签名 JWT | 返回 ErrInvalidSignature |\n| 错误 Audience | 返回 ErrInvalidAudience |\n| 登录成功 | 返回 AccessToken 和 RefreshToken |\n| 登录失败（错误密码） | 返回 401 |\n| Token 刷新成功 | 返回新的 AccessToken |\n| Token 刷新（过期 RefreshToken） | 返回 401 |\n\n### 8.3 测试覆盖率目标\n\n| 组件 | 目标覆盖率 |\n|------|-----------|\n| auth.go | 90% |\n| jwt.go (new) | 90% |\n\n---\n\n## 9. 实施计划\n\n### Phase 1: 核心功能\n- [ ] 定义 JWTConfig 配置结构\n- [ ] 实现 JWTManager 核心逻辑\n- [ ] 实现 Token 签发和验证\n\n### Phase 2: API 端点\n- [ ] 实现 /login 端点\n- [ ] 实现 /refresh 端点\n\n### Phase 3: 中间件\n- [ ] 实现 JWT 中间件\n- [ ] 配置公开端点列表\n- [ ] 实现 Claims 传递到 Context\n\n### Phase 4: 密钥管理\n- [ ] 实现 HS256 对称密钥支持\n- [ ] 实现 RS256 非对称密钥支持\n\n### Phase 5: 监控和测试\n- [ ] 添加 Prometheus 指标\n- [ ] 编写单元测试\n- [ ] 集成测试\n\n---\n\n## 10. 依赖\n\n### 10.1 外部依赖\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | ^5.0.0 | JWT token handling |\n| `github.com/prometheus/client_golang/prometheus` | ^1.16.0 | Metrics |\n\n### 10.2 内部依赖\n\n| Module | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router` | Existing router module |\n\n---\n\n## 11. 参考\n\n- [Delta Spec: AR-011](changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md)\n- [Proposal](proposal.md)\n- [AR-010: Router Session Management](pkg/router/design.md)\n- [JWT RFC 7519](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519)\n- [golang-jwt library](https://github.com/golang-jwt/jwt)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-